            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Most high-performing webinars run between 45 and 60 minutes: 30-40 minutes of presentation followed by 15-20 minutes of live Q&A. Anything over 90 minutes sees significant drop-off unless it is a hands-on workshop format.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
