              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Industry benchmarks put live attendance at 35-45% of registrants. If you send a replay, total consumption can reach 60-70% of all sign-ups. Low attendance (under 20%) usually signals a weak email nurture sequence or a topic mismatch.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
