            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Popular platforms include Zoom Webinars, Demio, GoTo Webinar, and Livestorm. Choose based on audience size, interactivity features (polls, breakout rooms), native CRM integrations, and whether you need automated on-demand replays.</p></div></div>
